1
0:00:12.958,000 --> 0:00:14,000
So when I was in Morocco,

2
0:00:15.158,000 --> 0:00:17,000
in Casablanca, not so long ago,

3
0:00:17.692,000 --> 0:00:21,000
I met a young unmarried mother called Faiza.

4
0:00:22.168,000 --> 0:00:25,000
Faiza showed me photos of her infant son

5
0:00:25.505,000 --> 0:00:31,000
