139
0:08:09.863,000 --> 0:08:11,000
Double standards for men and women,

140
0:08:12.551,000 --> 0:08:15,000
sex as a source of shame,

141
0:08:15.81,000 --> 0:08:19,000
family control limiting individual choices,

142
0:08:19.961,000 --> 0:08:22,000
and a vast gulf between appearance and reality:

143
0:08:23.708,000 --> 0:08:24,000
what people are doing

144
0:08:25.294,000 --> 0:08:27,000
and what they're willing to admit to,

145
0:08:27.639,000 --> 0:08:3,000
and a general reluctance to move beyond private whispers

146
0:08:31.615,000 --> 0:08:35,000
to a serious and sustained public discussion.

147
0:08:35.703,000 --> 0:08:38,000
As one doctor in Cairo summed it up for me,

148
0:08:39.192,000 --> 0:08:42,000
"Here, sex is the opposite of sport.

149
0:08:42.517,000 --> 0:08:44,000
Football, everybody talks about it,

150
0:08:44.683,000 --> 0:08:45,000
